Invocation Name: dementia care information
des: This skill provides information about how Dementia Care Specialists in every county of the state of Wisconsin can help those dealing with the challenges associated with dementia. The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment, or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
